  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time server-rendered HTML with minimal diffs over WebSocket",
    "Declarative HEEx templating language with components and slots",
    "Stateful LiveView and LiveComponent abstractions",
    "Built-in form validation and file upload support",
    "JavaScript interoperability with client-side hooks and commands",
    "Live navigation without full page reloads",
    "Async operations with loading states",
    "Comprehensive testing utilities",
    "Change tracking for optimized updates"
